snippet.title: Johnny Depp libel trial: actor denies repeatedly slapping Amber Heard | 5 News
snippet.description:
► Subscribe to 5 News: http://bit.ly/5NewsSub 

► A court has heard how Johnny Depp repeatedly slapped his ex-wife Amber Heard because she laughed at his tattoo.

The Hollywood star has been in the witness box in London for the second day in his libel case against The Sun. Depp is suing the newspaper’s publisher for an article describing as a wife-beater, a claim he denies.

Warning: this report contains details of alleged abuse and drug taking.
 
► Johnny Depp trial: Actor brands The Sun 'wife-beater' claims as 'complete lies'
